lexa.core.data

Class HashDataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • lexa.core.data.BaseDataSet
      • lexa.core.data.HashDataSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<DataItem>, DataSet

    public class HashDataSet
extends BaseDataSet
    A data set using hashed keys to access the content A DataSet that utilises a HashMap for storing the items. This class should be used in favour of the SimpleDataSet when there are a large number of entries or the entries will be accessed randomly and by key. NBThis performance of this class is poor when using iterators and iterator based functions
    Since:
    2016-09
    Author:
    William
